      "description": "每条折线表示以该时间点为终点、固定 5 分钟窗口内的滚动比率；图例 Last 为最新 5 分钟窗口值。",
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "pluginVersion": "9.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "influxdb",
            "uid": "${DS_INFLUXDB}"
          },
          "query": "from(bucket: \"${bucket}\")\n  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r[\"_measurement\"] == \"${measurement}\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r[\"_classify\"] == \"document\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r[\"_field\"] == \"_count\")\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r[\"_key\"] =~ /:download_total$/ or r[\"_key\"] =~ /:download_success$/ or r[\"_key\"] =~ /:download_exception$/ or r[\"_key\"] =~ /:parser_exception$/)\n  |> filter(fn: (r) => r[\"project\"] =~ /^${project:regex}$/ and r[\"spider\"] =~ /^${spider:regex}$/ and r[\"hostname\"] =~ /^${host:regex}$/)\n  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with metric: if r[\"_key\"] =~ /:download_success$/ then \"success\" else if r[\"_key\"] =~ /:download_exception$/ then \"dexc\" else if r[\"_key\"] =~ /:parser_exception$/ then \"pexc\" else \"total\" }))\n  |> group(columns: [\"metric\"])\n  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: sum, createEmpty: true)\n  |> toFloat()\n  |> fill(value: 0.0)\n  |> timedMovingAverage(every: 1m, period: 5m)\n  |> keep(columns: [\"_time\", \"_value\", \"metric\"])\n  |> pivot(rowKey: [\"_time\"], columnKey: [\"metric\"], valueColumn: \"_value\")\n  |> map(fn: (r) => {\n      total = if exists r.total then r.total else 0.0\n      success = if exists r.success then r.success else 0.0\n      dexc = if exists r.dexc then r.dexc else 0.0\n      pexc = if exists r.pexc then r.pexc else 0.0\n      return { _time: r._time, \"下载成功率\": if total > 0.0 then success / total else 0.0, \"下载异常率\": if total > 0.0 then dexc / total else 0.0, \"解析异常率\": if total > 0.0 then pexc / total else 0.0 }\n  })",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "请求下载趋势",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
